      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the choux and bake, 30 to 35 minutes",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Preheat the oven to 200°C fan. Melt the {{unsalted-butter}} (pastry amount) with the {{sea-salt-fine}} and 240 ml cold water in a saucepan. Bring to a rolling boil. Remove from the heat and beat in the {{plain-flour}} all at once until the dough pulls away from the sides. Dry out over the heat for 1 minute. Cool for 5 minutes, then beat in the {{eggs}} gradually until the paste is glossy and drops reluctantly from the spoon. Pipe 10 cm fingers onto lined baking trays, spacing well apart. Bake for 30 to 35 minutes until deep gold. Pierce each shell at one end, then return to the switched-off oven for 3 minutes to dry. Cool completely on a rack.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Fill and glaze",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Whip the {{double-cream}} (filling amount) with the {{icing-sugar}} and {{vanilla-extract}} to soft peaks. Split each éclair lengthways or pipe cream through the pierced end. For the glaze, heat the {{double-cream}} (glaze amount) until just steaming. Pour over the {{dark-chocolate}} and rest 30 seconds, then stir smooth. Stir in the {{unsalted-butter}} (glaze amount). Cool to 30°C. Dip the top of each filled éclair into the ganache. Set on a rack for 5 minutes before serving.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
